Notes:
    If a number is evenly divisible by 2 with no remainder,
then it is even. You can calculate the remainder with the modulo
operator % like this num % 2 == 0 .
If a number divided by 2 leaves a remainder of 1,
then the number is odd. You can check for this using num % 2 == 1 .
    We can click on the starting bracket to check the ending bracket, intellij is going to highlight the ending bracket.
    We can double click on inside any if condition to highlight all the code under the condition.
    We can shortcuts like Ctrl+Alt+L(windows) and Comm+Opt+L


Scanner Class:
    Scanner class is used to take the input of the user from the keyword.


